Ext.data.JsonP['About_the_Debug_perspective']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>About the Debug perspective</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-30083106\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>About the Debug perspective</h1>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083106_AbouttheDebugperspective-Chapters\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Chapters</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"toc-indentation \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/About_the_Debug_perspective-section-src-30083106_AbouttheDebugperspective-Introduction\">Introduction</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/About_the_Debug_perspective-section-src-30083106_AbouttheDebugperspective-Instructions\">Instructions</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/About_the_Debug_perspective-section-src-30083106_AbouttheDebugperspective-RelatedTopics\">Related Topics</a>    </p>\n</li></ul>    <p>This page gives an overview of the Debug perspective.    </p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083106_AbouttheDebugperspective-Introduction\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Introduction</span></h2>\n    <p>Switch to the Debug perspective when you want to debug the JavaScript code on one of your web pages. The Debug perspective contains several views that are not found in the Web perspective:    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><strong class=\" \">Debug View</strong> - The Debug View displays debugging targets and processes that are currently running.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><strong class=\" \">Variables View</strong> - The Variables View shows the scope of variables when the JavaScript thread is suspended.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><strong class=\" \">Breakpoints View</strong> - The Breakpoints View lists the breakpoints for the file that you are debugging.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><strong class=\" \">Scripts View</strong> - The Scripts View displays the scripts that are currently being debugged.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><strong class=\" \">Expressions View</strong> - The Expressions View displays the value of current expressions.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><strong class=\" \">AJAX Monitor View</strong> - The AJAX Monitor View displays current AJAX requests triggered inside browser during current debug session.    </p>\n</li></ul>    <p>In additon to the above debugging-specific views, you will also have access to some views from the Web perspective that you are probably familiar with:    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><strong class=\" \">Editor</strong> - The Editor area displays the file currently being debugged in its appropriate Editor.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><strong class=\" \">Outline View</strong> - The Outline View displays an outline of the code for the file that is currently being debugged.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><strong class=\" \">Console View</strong> - The Console View displays log output from the debugger.    </p>\n</li></ul>    <p>    <img src=\"images/download/attachments/30083106/DebugPerspective.png\" alt=\"images/download/attachments/30083106/DebugPerspective.png\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image\">\n        </img></p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083106_AbouttheDebugperspective-Instructions\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Instructions</span></h2>\n    <p>To switch to the Debug perspective:    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Click the <strong class=\" \">Perspective</strong> button     <img src=\"images/download/attachments/30083106/IconPerspective.png\" alt=\"images/download/attachments/30083106/IconPerspective.png\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image\">\n in the upper-right corner of the workbench.    </img></p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Select <strong class=\" \">Other &gt; Debug</strong>.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Click <strong class=\" \">OK</strong>.    </p>\n</li></ol>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083106_AbouttheDebugperspective-RelatedTopics\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Related Topics</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Installing_the_JavaScript_debugger\">Installing the JavaScript debugger</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Running_the_debugger\">Running the debugger</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Stepping_into_and_over_functions\">Stepping into and over functions</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Adding_a_breakpoint\">Adding a breakpoint</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Using_the_Console_View\">Using the Console View</a>    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=30083106\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"About the Debug perspective"});